column2: "My stomach's empty now that we made so many copies."
"Yep. So let's eat at least one of them! Nom nom~!"
"What? Whatwhatwhat? We aimed for the ARKS and caught [Elder] instead?"
"It's a good bargain -- a steal! Let's eat him up just like that!"
"Don't get cocky, [Double]...! I'll crush your expectations!"
"Whoa! W-whoawhoawhoa! You're trying to rend space with brute force? Are you an idiot? A moron?"
"You're trying to send us flying?! As expected of an idiot -- no, the apex of all idiots. Are you trying to die? Trying to get yourself killed?!"
"S-sir Gettemhart!"
"No! You shall not! I am Dark Falz [Elder]! Do not refer to me by that weak name!"
"If you believe yourself the refuse of the ARKS, then... seek the future with your own hands! Cast aside your resignation! Do not be bound by the past!"
"Then, you shall see the conclusion you've expected! Isn't that right?"
"That's why... don't become like me... Dia..."
"Y-yes, Sir Gettemhart!"
"That guy, at the end he said your name. Perhaps... he was still..."
"It's alright, Sir Zeno. <%me>. It's okay now."
"...as that person said, I am Melrondia. And that, itself, is good."
"I see."
"Wa--! Sis!"
"Don't touch me! I'm... not your sister!"
"But... I'm... I'm not a Dark Falz either so... I... what am I..?"
"Yuku!"
"Ehehhe... she got away again."
"It's alright. I won't give up. One day, I'll get through to her."
"No matter where she goes, I'll find her. Sis may have forgotten, but I'm skilled at finding things."
"That's because I've always been finding her stuff."
"Even now, it's the same. I'll definitely find her."
